headline.main: Sam Querrey Beats Rafael Nadal in Mexican Open Final
headline.print_headline: Sam Querrey Beats Rafael Nadal in Mexican Open Final

lead_paragraph: American Sam Querrey used a strong serve to beat Rafael Nadal 6-3, 7-6 (3) on Saturday night in the Mexican Open final.
